movie_title: Star Wars: Episode I - The Phantom Menace
title: I really enjoyed 'Phantom Menace' and I plan to see it again.
review: I thoroughly enjoyed 'Phantom Menace' even though I am not what you might call a 'Star Wars Person'.  I went to see it just because everyone else was, but I was pleasantly surprised by the whole movie.  The acting was great and the story was very interesting, especially having seen the original 'Star Wars'.
